+ * vid_console_color() - convert a color code to a pixel's internal
+ * representation
+ *
+ * The caller has to guarantee that the color index is less than
+ * VID_COLOR_COUNT (= 16).
+ *
+ * @priv	private data of the console device
+ * @idx		color index
+ * @return	color value
+ */
